snippet.title: One Sentence: Johnny Depp, Amber Heard, and an Important Warning about 'Cancel Culture'
snippet.description:
Jonny Depp increasingly looks to have been the victim in his relationship with Amber Heard. This is an opportunity to demystify male victims of IPV and to reassert the necessity of believing evidence over people and preserving the principle of 'innocent until proven guilty', and not just in court.

The only way to be sure of getting updates is my email list: https://groups.google.com/forum/#!forum/postmortem-studios-fan-group/join

Please like, subscribe and help grow the channel by recommending videos you like (or dislike) to your friends.

A lot of the time I use Teknoaxe music, so it's easier to put the attribution here all the time! http://teknoaxe.com/Home.php
If it's not Teknoaxe, it's probably Bass Rebels, here on Youtube.
